<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5046876>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Cephetola males. C. wologizi, holotype. A, upperside; B, underside. C. wologizi, paratype. C, upperside; D, underside. C. aurealiae, holotype, DRC. E, upperside, F, underside. The latter was accessed through the online type collection of RMCA (see link at the list of examined material)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5046876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5046880>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Cephetola male genitalia. C. wologizi, holotype, gen. prep.: SAFI00385.A, lateral view; C, aedeagus. C. aureliae, holotype. B, lateral view, D, aedeagus (reproduced from Libert’s original drawing (Libert 1999)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5046880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5046884>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Type localities of C. wologizi and C. praecox and known localities of C. obscuralis, C. obscuralis ssp. (sensu Libert 2020) and C. aureliae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5046884/files/figure.png" ;
